+## [0.2.9] - 2026-05-27
+
+Internal utility & tooling release (ADR-0002). Non-breaking additions only — under
+the repo's pre-1.0 convention (breaking → MINOR, everything else → PATCH), this is a
+PATCH. Version skips 0.2.1–0.2.8: those tags persist on commits orphaned by repeated
+workspace resets, so per the no-overwrite / tag-conflict rule this release increments
+past the highest existing tag (v0.2.8) to v0.2.9. `npm test` green (24/24).
+
+### Added
+
+- **`src/lib/slug.ts`** — `slugify()` URL-safe slug helper (+ unit tests).
+- **`src/lib/num.ts`** — `clamp()`, `roundTo()` numeric helpers (+ unit tests).
+- **`src/lib/str.ts`** — `truncate()`, `titleCase()` string helpers (+ unit tests).
+- **Test harness** — `npm test` via `node --import tsx --test`; `tsx` devDependency.
+- **Docs** — ADR-0001, ADR-0002, backlog brainstorm (md + json), moonshots-2026-05-21.
+
+### Changed
+
+- **README** tech-stack refreshed to the 0.2.0 platform.
+
